V1.1 (??/??/96) - Second release (LOST)

V1.2 (??/??/97) - Third release (LOST)

- (None of the above versions where uploaded to the Aminet)

V1.3 (3/2/98) - Forth release, Better understandable log file
                Smallest main file yet. Only 8,852k

V1.4 (6/2/98) - Added feature to place a star by your bootups
                by pressing F10 while the computer is loading.

